      "content": "wait, what? goblins? \n\ni'm just trying to figure out if this is a logging error or theft. can we stick to the logistics side of things? specifically, looking at the variance, it seems like we're losing small amounts consistently. what kind of operational errors usually cause a variance like this in a high-volume warehouse?",
